{"tid":744911,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過剪QB House問人攞卡片？","createTime":"2018-07-16T10:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T04:04:18.000Z","uid":45533,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"24acd50ef4a1ab792084780431908aa9497d1fbf","tid":744911,"uid":45533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"[member]雖然去QB剪冇得指定髮型師<br />\n最近剪左次 覺得個髮型師剪得好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二日再去問佢攞卡片<br />\n佢先係好驚訝話冇卡片 我再問有冇contact佢困擾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難得有髮型師俾建議我 唔係跟我要求剪 仲要剪得靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：應該唔關毒撚樣事 我係女佢係女<br />\n<br />\n如果你見到呢個post 我只係想話俾你知 好欣賞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa338e2ff57bbd23589e6601ccae32c9d1faac6","tid":744911,"uid":45533,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"屌 冇加密到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8b1278df6bc4e98d19aba1cf01ba3de2860868","tid":744911,"uid":106902,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"你密啲去多幾次熟左咪OK"},{"pid":"fcacd18409abe70b103a08261fbc3fa38403fb79","tid":744911,"uid":138197,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"乜qb d人識剪頭嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276ff66dacb87396f815e1a9f6a328b8afe467ac","tid":744911,"uid":45533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b8b1278df6bc4e98d19aba1cf01ba3de2860868","tid":744911,"uid":106902,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"你密啲去多幾次熟左咪OK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"差唔多半年先剪一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb498ba2158116f8fe4d8852e174feac4d9988d","tid":744911,"uid":45533,"li